Package: stancer
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Title: Stance Analysis using Ensemble of LLM Agents Through `ellmer`
Description: Tools for stance analysis using an ensemble of large language models. The package follows a multi-stage process in which different agents perform linguistic analysis, role-play as domain experts, and engage in structured debates to reach a final judgment. It works with 'ellmer' chat objects, so a user can choose which models and providers to use. Each result includes the full reasoning and intermediate steps from the agents.
